Pineapple Honey glazed Hamü´∂üèæGlaze:
1 cups Pineapple juice 
1/2 cup brown sugar 
1/3 cup honey
1/2 tsp cloves 
1/2 tsp cinnamon 
1/4 cup mustard
For base: 
8 Pineapple slices 

- [ ] Bake spiral ham for on 350 F 30 minutes covered.
- [ ] Uncover and Base with juices then bake uncovered for an additional 30 minutes.
